DecSoft App Builder

DecSoft App Builder allows you to create modern HTML5 apps, WebApps, Progressive WebApps, Web Extensions and Hybrid apps for both mobile and desktop platforms.

DecSoft HTML Compiler

DecSoft HTML Compiler compiles your modern HTML apps into executables for both Microsoft Windows 32 and 64 bits. Your app files are never extracted into the user's computer and run in a modern browser environment.
